AddToMenu Window-Ops
+ "$[gt.&Move]"              Move
+ "$[gt.&Resize]"            Resize
+ "$[gt.R&aise]"             Raise
+ "$[gt.&Lower]"             Lower
+ "$[gt.(De)&Iconify]"       Iconify
+ "$[gt.(Un)&Stick]"         Stick
+ "$[gt.(Un)Ma&ximize]"      Maximize
+ ""                         Nop
+ "$[gt.&Close]"             Close
+ "$[gt.&Destroy]"           Destroy
#+ "Thumbnail"                Thumbnail


AddToMenu RootMenu "Root Menu" Title
+ "AutoCon&figure screens" AutoConf
+ "Re&fresh Screen"        Refresh
+ "Re&start WM"		   Restart
+ "E&xit WM"		   Quit
